<subSubSection id="C301F0D2FFA7FF88A3A9FF36FD38664D" pageId="20" pageNumber="471" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BA4A359FFA7FF88A3A9FF36FD38664D" blockId="20.[151,1436,150,285]" pageId="20" pageNumber="471">
<emphasis id="B96F7F4BFFA7FF88A3A9FF36FE9C6785" bold="true" box="[151,256,187,213]" pageId="20" pageNumber="471">Remark.</emphasis>
The material from Berkane (
<bibRefCitation id="EF8ADEA8FFA7FF88A179FF36FCA86785" author="Berrahou, A. &amp; Chavanon, G. &amp; Richoux, P." box="[583,820,187,213]" pageId="20" pageNumber="471" pagination="44 - 50" refId="ref25291" refString="Berrahou, A., Chavanon, G. &amp; Richoux, P. (2000) Etudes sur la basse Moulouya (Maroc Oriental): 6. Les Coleopteres aquatiques de l'Oued Zegzel. Bulletin Mensuel de la Societe Linneenne de Lyon, 69 (3), 44 - 50. https: // doi. org / 10.3406 / linly. 2000.11320" type="journal article" year="2000">
Berrahou 
<emphasis id="B96F7F4BFFA7FF88A186FF36FD6D6785" box="[696,753,187,213]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="471">et al.</emphasis>
2000
</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation id="EF8ADEA8FFA7FF88A001FF36FBAF6785" author="Chavanon, G. &amp; Berrahou, A. &amp; Millan, A." box="[831,1075,187,213]" pageId="20" pageNumber="471" pagination="143 - 162" refId="ref25728" refString="Chavanon, G., Berrahou, A. &amp; Millan, A. (2004) Apport a la connaissance des Coleopteres et Hemipteres aquatiques du Maroc Oriental: Catalogue faunistique. Boletin de la Sociedad Entomologica Aragonesa (S. E. A.), 35, 143 - 162." type="journal article" year="2004">
Chavanon 
<emphasis id="B96F7F4BFFA7FF88A086FF36FC6C6785" box="[952,1008,187,213]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="471">et al.</emphasis>
2004
</bibRefCitation>
), where the species was cited as being from, have now been revised and it corresponds to 
<taxonomicName id="4C1BD8DAFFA7FF88A074FF52FBDF67A9" authorityName="Delgado &amp; Jach" authorityYear="2007" box="[842,1091,223,249]" class="Insecta" family="Hydraenidae" genus="Ochthebius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="20" pageNumber="471" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="judemaesi">
<emphasis id="B96F7F4BFFA7FF88A074FF52FBDF67A9" box="[842,1091,223,249]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="471">Ochthebius judemaesi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. Furthermore, 
<taxonomicName id="4C1BD8DAFFA7FF88A7D5FF52FA0067A8" authorityName="Saint-Claire Deville" authorityYear="1914" box="[1259,1436,223,249]" class="Insecta" family="Hydraenidae" genus="Ochthebius" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="20" pageNumber="471" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="semisericeus">
<emphasis id="B96F7F4BFFA7FF88A7D5FF52FB6367A9" box="[1259,1279,223,249]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="471">O</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis id="B96F7F4BFFA7FF88A633FF52FA0067A8" box="[1293,1436,223,248]" italics="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="471">semisericeus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
had already been excluded by 
<bibRefCitation id="EF8ADEA8FFA7FF88A124FE8EFD3C664D" author="Jach, M. A." box="[538,672,259,285]" pageId="20" pageNumber="471" pagination="45 - 53" refId="ref26683" refString="Jach, M. A. (2001) Revision of the Palearctic species of the genus Ochthebius XVIII. The European species of the O. semisericeus complex (Coleoptera: Hydraenidae). Entomological Problems, 32, 45 - 53." type="journal article" year="2001">Jäch (2001)</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
